reviewText: This DVD was a complete duplicate from other Cheaters DVDs. Nothing new included in set. Most of #2 have the same clips.

The Title"Uncensored" gives an impression that it has a content that you would no be able to see on TV. I would say 99% you could see on regular TV. There's some cursing(not much)and a flash of nudity. You can see more on HBO.. The advantage is no commercials.
